Introduction

This report details data collected from 2023-01-01 to 2023-06-26 by the Colorado State University (CSU) Agriculture Water Quality Program (AWQP). For more information, please contact AJ Brown at Ansley.Brown@colostate.edu or visit the CSU AWQP Website at https://waterquality.colostate.edu.

Notes

A value of 0 represents a no detect TSS, EC, and pH are done in house while the rest of the analytes are done through ALS
